O le Cell Cell Collective e avanoa saoloto mo le faʻaaogaina e le atunuʻu suʻesuʻe ma le leai ni tupe mama. O le faʻaaogaina o le Cell Cellive i totonu o faʻapupe-tupe e ono manaʻomia ai maliega faʻapitoa mo laisene. Faamolemole faafesootaʻi le support@cellcollective.org mo nisi faʻamatalaga.

Landing.ColumnBanner.BuildModelsDescript: Faʻataʻitaʻiga le tele o faʻalapotopotoga, e aofia ai fesoʻotaiga faʻavavelaʻau, faʻatonutonuga o le gene, faʻaliliuga o faʻaliliuga, fesoʻotaiga vavalalata i le cell cell, meaʻai, etc. e fesoʻotaʻi ma meaola eseese e afua mai siama i siama e felelei ai laau i tagata. Faʻamatala faʻataʻitaʻiga e aunoa ma le manaʻoga e ulufale pe fesuisuiai fomaʻi matatātā faigata.
Landing.ColumnBanner.PerformStimulations: Faʻaaoga le taimi moni, faʻataʻitaʻiga fefaʻasoaaʻi e faʻasaga i le faʻaogaina o le faʻaogaina o le ola i lalo o le tele o mea faʻapitoa faʻapea foʻi ma le fetuunaiga (pe a maʻi). Faʻateleina le faitau selau o suʻesuʻega faʻataʻitaʻi i se mataupu o minute ma faʻatino le suʻega o mea e faʻaogaina-faʻapitoa e faʻafofoga i tali faʻapitonuʻu i lalo o tulaga eseese
Landing.ColumnBanner.AnalyzeResultsDescr: Iloilo le faʻaogaina ma tali o auala faʻavae i lalo o tulaga eseese. Faʻasalalau faʻasalalauga faʻalavelave faʻalavelave faʻapitoa e vaʻai ma faʻatumauina aafiaga o tagata taitoatasi ma faʻapotopotoga o vaega i luga o le masini. Fuafua ma suʻesuʻe toe faʻaaogaina fualaau faʻataʻitaʻi ma le faʻaaogaina o le faʻataʻitaʻiga.
Landing.VideoBanner.VideoBannerDescripti: E le toe manaʻomia e tamaiti aoga le taulotoina o manatu faʻavae - e mafai ona latou faʻataʻitaʻi ma faʻatautaia fegalegaleaiga faʻamalosi nai lo le faʻaaogaina o le polokalama o le faʻaaogaina o le Cell Cellive.

JoyDashboardRide.joyrideStepsModelPhase2: <span> Conditions (poʻo SubConditions) e faʻaaogaina e faʻataʻitaʻiina ai felagolagomai poʻo le faʻaaogaina o mea faʻalagolago i le va o se tasi pe sili atu paaga fegalegaleaiga. Kiliki i luga o le faʻaopoopoga o le atigipusa e tatalaina ai le Faʻatonuga o vaega, toso ma faʻafaʻamau vaega talafeagai i le (faʻailoga vaega) faʻatalatalanoaga faʻamaonia ma faʻamaonia pe afai o le Tuʻu e tatau ona Faʻamasino pe le toaga. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.ClickO: O faʻataʻitaʻiga o loʻo faʻamatalaina ma faʻasino i le faʻaaogaina o le Poto Knowledge. Kiliki i luga o le {photo1} e faaopoopo ai mea e maua ma {photo2} e faaopoopo ai faʻasino. Faʻasalala ona ulufale i le PubMed Identifier (PMID) i le faʻasalalauga faʻasalalauga ma faʻapipiʻi faʻamatalaga. O faʻamatalaga e mafai ona tagotia e tusa ai ma le lomiga ma le ituaiga faʻamatalaga. Faʻasalaga saʻo i luga o le mau ma filifili le igoa e te manaʻo e faʻaopopo.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.Collab: O le galulue faʻatasi o le ki i mea fou e maua e faʻaogaina ai le auala - ma o loʻo i le fatu o le Cell Collective! O le kiliki i le {photo} e aveina oe i le itulau Faasoa, e mafai ai ona e faʻaopoopoina tagata galulue, fatuina sootaga fefaʻasoaʻi ma lolomi faʻataʻitaʻiga.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.Select: <span> Filifili le vaega e te manaʻo e sui. O le kilikiina o le atigipusa pe a fai o se suiga ole leiloa-o-function (ua faailoa mai e se moli moli), ma le kilikiina o le pusa e faalua ona avea ma sui-o-function mutation (o loo faailoa mai e se siaki lanu meamata). O le kiliki i le taimi lona tolu e aveesea ai le fesuiaiga. Mutuale e mafai ona faʻafeiloai muamua pe i le taimi o se faʻataʻitaʻiga e vaʻavaʻai ai i suiga i luga o le malosi i taimi moni. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase2.C: Kiliki {photo} e fatu ai se uluai setete. O le taimi lava e faia ai se uluai setete, o le a faʻaalia le faʻamaonia i totonu o le laupapa Faʻatonu. Mai lenei koluma, filifili vaega e te manaʻo e galue ai i le amataga o se simulation (t = 0).

Kiliki {photo} e faamaumauina se tafega simulation. O le a lanu le lanumeamata i le taimi o loʻo faʻaulu ai le lipine. Suiga i tulaga faataitai poo fesuiaiga, ma a latou vaitau taimi ole taimi ole taimi ole taimi ole taimi ole taimi ole taimi ole taimi ole taimi ole taimi ole taimi ole taimi ole taimi ole taimi ole taimi ole taimi ole taimi ole taimi.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase2.Mul: <span> E mafai ona filifili suʻega faʻapitoa e faʻaaoga ai taga siaki. Aʻo filifilia, e mafai ona e aveesea, kopi, pe toe faʻatautaia faʻataʻitaʻiga i le taimi e tasi. O lenei mea e sili ona aoga mo le faʻafouina o faʻataʻitaʻiga pe a uma ona faia se suiga i se faiga faʻavae faatonutonu. </ span>,
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase2.Col: Kiliki {photo} i tafatafa o Flow Flow: faaigoa e fatu ai se tafega simulation. E le mafai ona faamaumauina faʻataʻitaʻiga o simulation, o le mea lea, o tulaga i fafo (o mea e aofia ai) po o suiga, ma o latou tulaga (o taimi e tutupu ai taimi) e tatau ona muaʻi faʻamalamalamaina ma le lima. Faitau le faʻasologa o faʻasologa o faʻasologa mo faʻamatalaga atili.
